title: Looking For A One Bedroom - Porchlight Apartments
posting_body: Our beautiful property and comfortable floor plans also make it easy to move your four-legged friends to pet-friendly Porchlight Apartments.

Additional property amenities extend to an outdoor pool for when the sun is shining on Federal Way, as well as a heated indoor pool and hot tub.
We also offer private garages to park your vehicle.
Make the drive to Celebration Park for its trails and sports fields, or to the shops of Celebration Center.
From area shopping and dining to outdoor recreation at a park, everything you need is near this Federal Way community.
When you want to get out of Federal Way, you can head to other nearby cities in the Seattle metropolitan area, including the opportunity to soak in the vibrant downtown Seattle culture.
When it comes to a city lifestyle with the appeal of the suburbs, it's hard to top this great location.
